[Refraining from the prescribed referral to the health authorities for science-based postexposure treatment has again led to the tragic outcome. see Dutta LK. Disastrous results of indigenous methods of rabies prevention in developing countries. Int J Infect Dis 2002; 6: 236-237; https://core.ac.uk/download/pdf/82319514.pdf.

